\"value\\": \\"<p>Mozart and his father purchased or were given two souvenirs of their\\\\nencounter with Vesuvius, some lava and a copper engraving that shows a close-up\\\\nview of the erupting volcano. The lava they acquired does not survive; the\\\\nengraving they purchased or were given survives in the library of the Salzburg\\\\nMuseum:</p>\\"}, {\\"type\\": \\"paragraph\\", \\"value\\": \\"<p><br/></p><embed alt=\\\\\\": Undated engraving owned by the Mozart\\\\u2019s, Venus erupting (Salzburg, Salzburg Museum)\\\\\\" embedtype=\\\\\\"image\\\\\\" format=\\\\\\"fullwidth\\\\\\" id=\\\\\\"2\\\\\\"/>\\"}, {\\"type\\": \\"paragraph\\", \\"value\\": \\"<p>Some souvenirs acquired by, or given to, the Mozarts on their tours\\\\nthrough Europe are known only from descriptions in the Mozart family letters.\\\\u00a0</p>\\"}, {\\"type\\": \\"paragraph\\", \\"value\\": \\"<p><br/></p><embed alt=\\\\\\"Lava\\\\\\" embedtype=\\\\\\"image\\\\\\" format=\\\\\\"left\\\\\\" id=\\\\\\"3\\\\\\"/>\\"}, {\\"type\\": \\"paragraph\\", \\"value\\": \\"<p>Others, though, and in particular topographical engravings from London\\\\nand Naples, survive.\\\\u00a0</p>\\"}]", "locked": false, "title": "1. The Mozarts as Collectors of Souvenirs", "numchild": 0, "show_in_menus": false, "live": true, "seo_title": "", "search_description": "", "depth": 4, "latest_revision_created_at": "2017-09-18T14:33:19.982Z", "has_unpublished_changes": true, "content_type": 34, "path": "0001000100020001", "owner": 1, "pk": 11, "first_published_at": "2017-06-15T14:28:20.323Z", "url_path": "/home/souvenirs/second-example-page/", "expired": false, "slug": "second-example-page", "expire_at": null, "go_live_at": null}	\N	11	3
