35	f	2017-09-18 16:53:08.425503+01	{"body": "[{\\"type\\": \\"paragraph\\", \\"value\\": \\"<p>Later, during\\\\nthe family visits to Paris in 1763-1764 and London in 1764-1765, Leopold\\\\nproduced both visual and musical objects as souvenirs of Wolfgang Amadeus,\\\\nincluding portraits and printed music, and, in the case of the motet <i>God is our Refuge</i> K20, Mozart\\\\u2019s\\\\nautograph manuscript.\\\\u00a0</p>\\"}, {\\"type\\": \\"paragraph\\", \\"value\\": \\"<p><br/></p><embed alt=\\\\\\"God.is.our.refuge : Mozart manuscript\\\\\\" embedtype=\\\\\\"image\\\\\\" format=\\\\\\"fullwidth\\\\\\" id=\\\\\\"5\\\\\\"/>\\"}]", "locked": false, "title": "Examples of souvenirs produced by the Mozarts", "numchild": 0, "show_in_menus": false, "live": false, "seo_title": "", "search_description": "", "depth": 5, "latest_revision_created_at": "2017-09-18T15:48:03.611Z", "has_unpublished_changes": true, "content_type": 34, "path": "00010001000200020001", "owner": 3, "pk": 14, "first_published_at": null, "url_path": "/home/souvenirs/2-mozarts-producers-souvenirs/examples-souvenirs-produced-mozarts/", "expired": false, "slug": "examples-souvenirs-produced-mozarts", "expire_at": null, "go_live_at": null}	\N	14	3
221	f	2017-10-06 17:58:25.999989+01	{"search_description": "", "owner": 3, "latest_revision_created_at": "2017-09-22T16:45:04.882Z", "go_live_at": null, "title": "German-language text usages and understanding of \\u2018souvenir\\u2019 prior to 1800", "seo_title": "", "draft_title": "German-language text usages and understanding of \\u2018souvenir\\u2019 prior to 1800", "live": true, "last_published_at": "2017-09-22T16:45:04.882Z", "has_unpublished_changes": false, "body": "[{\\"type\\": \\"paragraph\\", \\"id\\": \\"debfa1a2-63f6-43cd-8e95-0e2e83c1e4c0\\", \\"value\\": \\"<p></p><h3>Me. La Roche, <i>Nouvelle Methode pour\\\\ntraiter la Grammaire fran\\\\u00e7oise, das ist: Neue Methode die Frantz\\\\u00f6sische\\\\nGrammatic zu tractiren</i> (22<sup>nd</sup> edition: Leipzig, 1751), 156 (\\\\u2018Et\\\\nje vous suis oblige Und ich bin euch verbunden de votre bon souvenir\\\\u2019) , 167,\\\\n169, 298, 303-4, 306-7, 317<br/></h3><p></p>\\\\u00a0<embed alt=\\\\\\"Me. La Roche, Nouvelle Methode (Leizpig, 1751), p. 156\\\\\\" embedtype=\\\\\\"image\\\\\\" format=\\\\\\"left\\\\\\" id=\\\\\\"12\\\\\\"/> \\\\n\\\\n<p><br/>\\\\n\\\\n</p><p><br/></p>\\\\n\\\\n<p></p>\\\\n\\\\n<p></p>\\"}, {\\"type\\": \\"paragraph\\", \\"id\\": \\"bdc17e79-da48-44a9-adba-4f9e1477d05f\\", \\"value\\": \\"<h3></h3><h3><p>Gottfried Ephraim M\\\\u00fcller, <i>Historisch-critische Einleitung zu n\\\\u00f6thiger\\\\nKenntni\\\\u00df und n\\\\u00fctzlichem Gebrauche der alten lateinischen Schriftsteller</i>\\\\n(Dresden, 1751), v.286</p><p><br/><i>Neues deutsch=franz\\\\u00f6sisch und lateinisches W\\\\u00f6rter=Buch</i> as part of Choffin, <i>Nouveau\\\\nDictionnaire du Voyageur, Fran\\\\u00e7ois\\\\u2014Allemand\\\\u2014Latin et Allemand\\\\u2014Fran\\\\u00e7ois\\\\u2014Latin </i>(Frankfurt,\\\\n1770), 40: \\\\u2018Andenken, m. le souvenir, la m\\\\u00e9moire\\\\u2019.<br/>Joh. Bernoulli, <i>Joh. Heinrich Lamberts . . . deutscher gelehrter Breifwechsel </i>(Berlin,\\\\n[1780s], i.327</p><p><br/>