59	f	2017-09-21 19:46:27.606974+01	{"body": "[{\\"type\\": \\"paragraph\\", \\"value\\": \\"According\\\\nto Grimm, before about 1800, \\\\u2018souvenir\\\\u2019 is rendered in German as \\\\u2018andenken\\\\u2019,\\\\nan evocation of thought and memory, and only secondarily, in importance, as an\\\\nobject (the latter idea more explicitly rendered as \\\\u00e4uszeres zeichen and,\\\\nlater, as \\\\u2019geschenk zur erinnerung\\\\u2019).<a href=\\\\\\"#_ftn1\\\\\\">[1]</a><p><p></p><p>#_ftn1</p></p>\\\\u00a0 \\\\n\\\\n<p><br/>\\\\n\\\\n<hr/>\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n<p>\\\\n\\\\n<p><a href=\\\\\\"#_ftnref1\\\\\\">[1]</a>\\\\u00a0\\\\n<a href=\\\\\\"http://woerterbuchnetz.de/cgi-bin/WBNetz/genFOplus.tcl?sigle=DWB&amp;lemid=GS32291\\\\\\">http://woerterbuchnetz.de/cgi-bin/WBNetz/genFOplus.tcl?sigle=DWB&amp;lemid=GS32291</a></p>\\\\n\\\\n</p>\\\\n\\\\n</p>\\"}, {\\"type\\": \\"paragraph\\", \\"value\\": \\"<h3><b>German-language text usages\\\\nof \\\\u2018souvenir\\\\u2019 prior to 1800\\\\u00a0</b></h3><p>Early, isolated instances of the word souvenir\\\\n(via the word <i>andenken</i> referring to\\\\nboth object and memory are Johann Beneroni and Carl Placardi, <i>Das\\\\nKaiserliche Sprach= un W\\\\u00f6rterbuch, darinnen die vier Europ\\\\u00e4ischen Hauptsprachen</i>\\\\n(K\\\\u00f6ln, 1766) and the <i>Neues\\\\ndeutsch=franz\\\\u00f6sisch und lateinisches W\\\\u00f6rter=Buch</i> in Choffin, <i>Nouveau Dictionnaire du Voyageur,\\\\nFran\\\\u00e7ois\\\\u2014Allemand\\\\u2014Latin et Allemand\\\\u2014Fran\\\\u00e7ois\\\\u2014Latin </i>(Frankfurt, 1770).\\\\u00a0</p>\\"}]", "locked": false, "title": "German understanding of souvenir", "numchild": 0, "show_in_menus": false, "live": false, "seo_title": "", "search_description": "", "depth": 5, "latest_revision_created_at": null, "has_unpublished_changes": false, "content_type": 34, "path": "00010001000200030001", "owner": 3, "pk": 17, "first_published_at": null, "url_path": "/home/souvenirs/sample-object-page/german-understanding-souvenir/", "expired": false, "slug": "german-understanding-souvenir", "expire_at": null, "go_live_at": null}	\N	17	3
